      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Goal\n\nDefine the **Goal** node type for planning graphs.\n\nQuestions to answer:\n- What makes a goal different from a task?\n- Is it strategic, local, or both?\n- What fields should it carry beyond label and markdown?\n- Should goals support priority or completion state?\n\nOutput:\n- clear purpose\n- canonical data shape\n- relationship rules",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
