      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Decision\n\nDefine the **Decision** node type.\n\nQuestions to answer:\n- How is a decision represented distinctly from discussion?\n- Should decisions carry rationale, status, and date?\n- Can a decision supersede an older decision?\n- How should decisions connect to tasks and constraints?\n\nOutput:\n- decision semantics\n- canonical data shape\n- precedence/update rules",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
