        "markdown": "## Risk / Edge Case\n\nDefine the **Risk / Edge Case** node type.\n\nQuestions to answer:\n- Should risk and edge case stay combined or split later?\n- Does this node track severity, likelihood, or mitigation?\n- How should edge cases connect to acceptance criteria and tasks?\n- When does a risk become a task or decision?\n\nOutput:\n- scope definition\n- canonical fields\n- escalation behavior",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
