      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Implementation Phase 1\n\nThis proposal updates the `manifest` and `dictionary` to officially support the planning primitives defined in the previous task.\n\n### Changes:\n- **Manifest**: Adds `goal`, `task`, `decision`, `constraint` to `nodeTypes`.\n- **Dictionary**: Injects `nodeDefs` for these types to provide schema enforcement.\n- **Linkage**: Connects planning nodes to execution ports.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": false,
